snippet.title: Gemstone Legends - Adventure begins now!
snippet.description:
Our world has been attacked by evil powers. Wizards summoned the eternal evil. Dark portals full of hordes of monsters are opening everywhere. You are the only hope to save these lands. Download the game and see if you can handle the challenge!

https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.gemstone.legends.rpg.adventure.game
